{"tid":1516041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【反CCTVB 總攻擊】#noTVBchallenge 正！式！啟！動！","createTime":"2019-08-29T11:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T02:16:22.000Z","uid":267969,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7b32220d541525dab7ee6256245355c148322be8","tid":1516041,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:55:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TVB愚惑大眾，幫黑警講說話，你係咪好嬲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過百員工聯署，李保安擺出WFC樣，你係咪好嬲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後編導被炒，連監製撐良心都同一命運，你係咪好想TVB執笠呀？</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好怕麻煩，做多一步<br />\n自己刪台，叫多幾個朋友刪台，影相話俾TVB廣告商知長期抵制！<br />\n越多人做越多壓力！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>#noTVBchallenge 玩法如下：</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少刪除TVB 81-85台其中一台，或者揼爛myTV SUPER，影相或拍片<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 將相片up上 FB 或 IG，tag三個朋友承接挑戰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Private post: 將相send俾一個TVB廣告客戶 <span style=\"color: red;\">OR</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Public post 用@ tag任何一個TVB廣告客戶 (用@，被tag嘅廣告商FB 將收到通知) <br />\n<br />\n(如果一早已經刪咗台嘅，就撳 &quot;Guide&quot; 掣影張相代替)<br />\n<br />\n****<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>出FB/ IG post Template:</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n#noTVBchallenge<br />\n無綫新聞，誤導市民，我要TVB執笠！<br />\n刪除TVB 81-85台其中一台，或者揼爛myTV SUPER<br />\n抵制TVB廣告客戶 @HiPP.hk<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/xSwayMF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxSwayMF.jpg&h=a041b4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. 朋友A<br />\n2. 朋友B<br />\n3. 朋友C<br />\n請接受挑戰！<br />\n<br />\nTVB廣告客戶名單: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JSJaQK&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=b3c31624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK</a><br />\n#noTVBchallenge<br />\n#無綫新聞 #出賣港人<br />\n#袁志偉下台 #黃淑明下台<br />\n#抵制TVB廣告客戶<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n呢個諗法抵制TVB團隊早喺7月頭已經有，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">10月TVB開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約</span></strong>，接近9月推#noTVBchallenge 係合適嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n唔似#Eye4HK 要自拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家會玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de913b5d7dcbb5d778fd05991fea21b9e502dc0","tid":1516041,"uid":267969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抵制TVB好Easy，LIKE數就是力量，嚇怕廣告商</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=c49b7c1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: sayno2tvb<br />\n<br />\nTVB廣告客戶google sheet 名單 (消費前諗清楚): <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=b59d5f71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a><br />\n<br />\nTG 抵制廣告行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=823cdcfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 狙擊活